Data is downloaded for 2000 and 2010 censuses. The variables and their levels are coded as they are on IPUMS-I documentation. Finally, the data is joined to the ethnic block classifications.

data_joined <- data %>% filter(YEAR %in% c(2000, 2010))

for (var in names(data_joined)[!endsWith(names(data_joined), "LOC")]) {
  tryCatch({
    list <- list()
    list[["names"]] <- names(attr(data_joined[[var]], "labels"))
    list[["keys"]] <- as.numeric(attr(data_joined[[var]], "labels"))

    
    data_joined[[var]] <- ifelse(
      data_joined[[var]] %in% list[["keys"]],
      list[["names"]][
        match(data_joined[[var]], list[["keys"]])
      ],
      data_joined[[var]]
    )

    #cat("FINISHED", var, "\n")
  },  error = function(e) {
    cat("ERROR in variable", var, ": ", e$message, "\n")
  })
}

marriages <- marriages %>%
  mutate(
    AgeMarried_F = case_when(
      is.na(AgeMarried_F) ~ 19,
      TRUE ~ AgeMarried_F
    ),
    AgeMarried_M = case_when(
      is.na(AgeMarried_M) ~ 25,
      TRUE ~ AgeMarried_M
    ),
    YearMarried = CensusYear - (Age_F - AgeMarried_F),
    YearsMarried = Age_F - AgeMarried_F
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    YearMarried = case_when(
      YearMarried > CensusYear ~ CensusYear,
      TRUE ~ YearMarried
    ),
    YearsMarried = case_when(
      YearsMarried < 0 ~ 0,
      TRUE ~ YearsMarried
    )
  )

The mean ages at first marriage are 19 for women and 25 for men, which serve as the imputation for missing values.

urban_rural <- data_joined %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  filter(CensusYear == 2000) %>%
  select(CensusYear, Const, Urban) %>%
  group_by(Const, Urban) %>%
  mutate(Urban = case_when(Urban == "Urban" ~ "1", Urban == "Rural" ~ "0", TRUE ~ Urban)) %>%
  mutate(Urban = as.integer(Urban)) %>%
  group_by(Const) %>%
  summarise(
    UrbanCount = sum(Urban), 
    Population = n()
  ) %>%
  mutate(Urbanization = UrbanCount / Population)

urban_rural <- urban_rural %>% select(Const, Urbanization)

hhi_by_decade_ethnic <- function(data, decade, combined_df = NULL) {
  ethnic_proportions <- data %>%
    group_by(Const, Ethnicity) %>%
    summarise(ConstEthnicPopulation = n(), .groups = "keep") %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    group_by(Const) %>%
    mutate(
      ConstPopulation = sum(ConstEthnicPopulation),
      Proportion = ConstEthnicPopulation / ConstPopulation,
      DecadeMarried = decade
    )
  
  write.csv(ethnic_proportions, paste0("exports/ethnicity_proportions/ethnicity_proportions_", decade, ".csv"), row.names = FALSE)
  
  if (is.null(combined_df)) {
    combined_df <- ethnic_proportions
  } else {
    combined_df <- bind_rows(combined_df, ethnic_proportions)
  }
  
  return(combined_df)
}

combined_hhi <- NULL
combined_hhi <- hhi_by_decade_ethnic(hhi_1950s, "1951-1960", combined_hhi)

combined_hhi <- hhi_by_decade_ethnic(hhi_2000s, "2001-2010", combined_hhi)

write.csv(combined_hhi, "exports/combined_ethnicity_const_hhi.csv", row.names = FALSE)
hhi_by_decade_block <- function(data, decade, combined_df = NULL) {
  ethnic_proportions <- data %>%
    group_by(Const, EthnicBlock) %>%
    summarise(ConstBlockPopulation = n(), .groups = "keep") %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    group_by(Const) %>%
    mutate(
      ConstPopulation = sum(ConstBlockPopulation),
      Proportion = ConstBlockPopulation / ConstPopulation,
      DecadeMarried = decade
    )
  
  write.csv(ethnic_proportions, paste0("exports/ethnic_block_proportions/ethnic_block_proportions_", decade, ".csv"), row.names = FALSE)
  
  if (is.null(combined_df)) {
    combined_df <- ethnic_proportions
  } else {
    combined_df <- bind_rows(combined_df, ethnic_proportions)
  }
  
  return(combined_df)
}

combined_hhi <- NULL
combined_hhi <- hhi_by_decade_block(hhi_1950s, "1951-1960", combined_hhi)
combined_hhi <- hhi_by_decade_block(hhi_1960s, "1961-1970", combined_hhi)
combined_hhi <- hhi_by_decade_block(hhi_1970s, "1971-1980", combined_hhi)
combined_hhi <- hhi_by_decade_block(hhi_1980s, "1981-1990", combined_hhi)
combined_hhi <- hhi_by_decade_block(hhi_1990s, "1991-2000", combined_hhi)
combined_hhi <- hhi_by_decade_block(hhi_2000s, "2001-2010", combined_hhi)
